headline: Job Growth in U.S. Small Businesses Continues the Pace Seen in the Back Half of 2024
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., February 04, 2025--According to the Paychex Small Business Employment Watch, the pace of job growth in U.S. small businesses with fewer than 50 employees remained slightly below 100 in January, consistent with the last six months of 2024. Meanwhile, hourly earnings growth for workers decelerated to 2.87% in January, marking its first time starting the year below three percent since 2021.
